From: SeongJae Park <sj@kernel.org>
Date: Mon, 16 Mar 2026 18:07:31 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] mm/damon/sysfs: fixup: initialize damon_sysfs_context->pause

Fix "mm/damon/tests/core-kunit: test pause commitment".

Signed-off-by: SeongJae Park <sj@kernel.org>
---
 mm/damon/sysfs.c | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/mm/damon/sysfs.c b/mm/damon/sysfs.c
index 4cbb8b9aaba3c..7bd42dd8c4a73 100644
--- a/mm/damon/sysfs.c
+++ b/mm/damon/sysfs.c
@@ -879,6 +879,7 @@ static struct damon_sysfs_context *damon_sysfs_context_alloc(
 	context->kobj = (struct kobject){};
 	context->ops_id = ops_id;
 	context->addr_unit = 1;
+	context->pause = false;
 	return context;
 }
 
